        <li><strong>X (Twitter) API</strong> - Curated 11-account feed via official X API v2. Onchain primary (@lookonchain, @spotonchain, @arkham, @whale_alert), official exchange announcements (@binance, @coinbase, @CoinbaseAssets, @upbit_global), and newswire-speed macro (@DeItaone, @FirstSquawk, @DBdaily). 20s polling, retweets and replies filtered.</li>
